    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed per MRL 2 scoping rules. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all 5 evaluated operating points. Assessment team notes that validation data originate from the 2018 FDA benchmark campaign; the model was subsequently revised in January 2026 and no re-validation against updated experimental data was conducted, as the benchmark dataset is considered the authoritative reference for this device class.",
